description: This fully gut-renovated 2-family home features two spacious units, each offering 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Both units boast central A/C and heating, in-unit laundry, and modern kitchens equipped with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and white shaker cabinets.Located in a prime area, you’re just a short walk from the beach and public transportation. This turnkey property is ready to go, with a new roof, updated plumbing, and electrical systems, ensuring minimal maintenance for the new owner.Market rents are projected at $10,000 monthly, with renewal notices already sent out.  Don’t miss this exceptional investment opportunity!
